      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SNAPPER ROCKS (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (22.32) from Box 1 at this track. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Must come into calculations. UTAH GUNN (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by one length at Q Straight in a handy 19.24 beating Lost Your Marker. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. One of the leading chances again. LITTLE STARSKY (5) was a winner two back when racing on speed but drifted back latest and safely held when 8th and beaten 14 lengths at this track (22.56). Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. In the mix. ENTERTAINING (7) was in the money last start in fast time - poses a threat again.",
